        Get the CAPTCHA attributes as provided by the CAPTCHA provider plugin. The CAPTCHA provider plugin CAPTCHA attributes. Google's reCAPTCHA v2 CAPTCHA provider will provide 'siteKey' and Google's reCAPTCHA v3 CAPTCHA provider will provide 'siteKey' and 'action' to be able to invoke the challenge.
